    "Each attention check allowed one additional attempt.",
    "Participants who failed two attention checks were removed from all analyses (N = 2).",
    "After providing their responses to each task, participants answered demographics questions.",
    "GPT-4 procedural responses were generated through human-assistance facilitated by the first author, who provided each prompt in the following order: AUT, CT, and DAT.",
